highlights.text: Bruno Mars has the most spots on Top Songs Malaysia. “Die With A Smile” is the highest at #22.
“IRIS OUT” by Kenshi Yonezu is the highest new entry on Top Songs Malaysia at #163.
“Night Changes” by One Direction has been on Top Songs Malaysia the longest, at 1721 days straight.
“Harapan” by Hyper Act is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Malaysia, up 85 spots at #84.
